data.description: Living the dream at Eastlake Greens! Finally a rare opportunity to live at Fairway Villas at Eastlake Greens.  This community is nestled amongst green rolling fairways and golf carts. Best described as a private pocket conveniently located close to all.  Literally within five minutes from Otay Ranch Shopping Center, coffee shops, grocery store, Walmart, restaurants, schools, state route 125 and those conveniences most related to daily living.  The floor plan of this home has been modified to express an open floor plan that now allows the vaulted living room, kitchen, dining area and back patio to become one seamless space.  Enjoy the living room fireplace that brings a cozy vibe to the family hub.  Tasteful and modern colors will appeal to a discriminating buyer.  The spacious common area is reserved for the bottom level, while the bedrooms are in the privacy of the upstairs.  The master bedroom is spacious and you’ll enjoy a barn door entrance to the walk in closet.  An upstairs loft can be utilized as an office, a game area, a workout spot or a landing to decorate as a seating area.  The loft overlooks the vaulted living room and common family areas of the house to allow one to stay connected to family activity from the upstairs loft.  Step outside and enjoy the community pool or just take a long walk along the golf greens that surround this wonderful community.
